<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6073] Change CollectionAdminRequest to deprecate helper wrappers and move towards Builder design for CollectionsAPI calls</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6073</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the process also cleanup the following: The CollectionAdminRequest has a createCollection() method which has the following hard-coded:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;req.setRouterName(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;implicit&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a bug and we should remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
